                </div>
                <div class="stages-grid">
                    <div class="stage-card minor">
                        <div class="stage-level" style="color: #44AA44;">Minor Flooding</div>
                        <h3 class="stage-title">Action Stage</h3>
                        <div class="stage-description">
                            Minimal or no property damage, but possibly some public threat or inconvenience. Some overbank flooding of low-lying areas.
                        </div>
                        <div class="stage-actions">
                            <strong>Actions:</strong>
                            Monitor conditions, prepare supplies, avoid flooded roads
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="stage-card moderate">
                        <div class="stage-level" style="color: #FFDD44;">Moderate Flooding</div>
                        <h3 class="stage-title">Minor Flood Stage</h3>
                        <div class="stage-description">
                            Some inundation of structures and roads near streams. Evacuations of people and transfer of property to higher elevations may be necessary.
                        </div>
                        <div class="stage-actions">
                            <strong>Actions:</strong>
                            Prepare to evacuate, move valuables to higher floors, secure property
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="stage-card major">
                        <div class="stage-level" style="color: #FFAA44;">Major Flooding</div>
                        <h3 class="stage-title">Moderate Flood Stage</h3>
                        <div class="stage-description">
                            Extensive inundation and property damage. Large-scale evacuations and emergency services response required.
                        </div>
                        <div class="stage-actions">
                            <strong>Actions:</strong>
                            Evacuate immediately if ordered, avoid all flooded areas, emergency shelter
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="stage-card record">
                        <div class="stage-level" style="color: #FF4444;">Record Flooding</div>
                        <h3 class="stage-title">Major Flood Stage</h3>
                        <div class="stage-description">
                            Rare flooding with significant threat to life and property. Catastrophic damage expected. Emergency response fully activated.
                        </div>
                        <div class="stage-actions">
                            <strong>Actions:</strong>
                            Follow all evacuation orders, seek highest ground, emergency services only
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
